{"tid":2149041,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭連任機會大增- 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-10T08:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T14:08:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":279,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"a901a893ccca6313c7f82ae6fdce53844652bead","tid":2149041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:02:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/HUJV7IBUUBGFRDCLW3SQE7QZRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FHUJV7IBUUBGFRDCLW3SQE7QZRM%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=4dd35e50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FHUJV7IBUUBGFRDCLW3SQE7QZRM%2F&h=5fc0b75e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/HUJV7IBUUBGFRDCLW3SQE7QZRM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n林鄭連任機會大增- 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_eCx_1Rlb8Jxf1hxJa6bdTmC0gg=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LQFYB5HXFRBN7BTSH6MKL4H27A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_eCx_1Rlb8Jxf1hxJa6bdTmC0gg%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLQFYB5HXFRBN7BTSH6MKL4H27A.jpg&h=036ece4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美帝制裁中共十一忠臣，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭聲稱在美國沒有資產，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭最令人佩服的，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n影響兒子的人生，林鄭不介意；她在意的，是美國財政部侵犯私隱。觀乎十一忠臣反應，美國制裁最辣的一招，原來並不是凍結資產、禁止入境、令你大部分信用卡報廢（林鄭連八達通也不需要，當然不希罕信用卡），甚或驅逐你的親人，而是公開你的個人資料，問你怕未？<br />\n<br />\n根據那行政命令Sec.4(a)(i)，只要有人被美帝認定有份「開展、實施或執行」（developing, adopting, or implementing）港區國安法，就可以被制裁了。顯而易見，下任特首是沒可能不執行國安法的，即是說，他/她一上任，就可肯定自動登上這張邪惡的制裁榜。須知道不能用iPhone、子女不能留學美國，都是小事，最最最可怕的，是你以前的地址被洩漏！問世間，多少人能承受這樣大的打擊呢？美國太可恥了。<br />\n<br />\n要當未來特首，不但需要忠誠勇毅，還要無懼護照號碼被公開，相信很多人都過不了最後一關，必打退堂鼓。但林鄭卻完全達標。電影的歐陽鋒說，找刀客要找穿鞋子的；中央選特首，當然選名字上了榜的人吧。"},{"pid":"3b84dc0a7dc332f20443749cff13a49366594190","tid":2149041,"uid":43062,"like":267,"dislike":0,"score":267,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好換人，新特首必定有蜜月期<br />\n<br />\n攬炒之母唔係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878eae65fd548c13b8b8f77b370788ee49b627a8","tid":2149041,"uid":101507,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"講真邊個會想執依個爛攤子，自己全家仲會俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90555985c9fcbf3331f9ae5cbdaaabf1e939dcde","tid":2149041,"uid":2054,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"一做就全家制裁<br />\n一世係大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279d0b971834eeb89c3b075206fbf284d34dc3f1","tid":2149041,"uid":28155,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"878eae65fd548c13b8b8f77b370788ee49b627a8","tid":2149041,"uid":101507,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"講真邊個會想執依個爛攤子，自己全家仲會俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"十一哥 <br />\n陳自私"},{"pid":"a4fa256ac0a48380c1f1a2322ae7aa030a325c81","tid":2149041,"uid":134474,"like":95,"dislike":10,"score":85,"quote":{"pid":"878eae65fd548c13b8b8f77b370788ee49b627a8","tid":2149041,"uid":101507,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"講真邊個會想執依個爛攤子，自己全家仲會俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNw4YLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNw4YLZ.jpg&h=bc3c4b92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrdZNEk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%